    "description":  "If your organisation has published a modern slavery statement, you can use this service to add your statement to the registry.",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis service allows you to add your modern slavery statement to the government-run online modern slavery statement registry. You can use this service to:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eprovide a link to the modern slavery statement published on your organisation’s website\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eanswer questions about your statement\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003epublish this information on the ‘Find a modern slavery statement’ service\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"what-we-do-with-your-information\"\u003eWhat we do with your information\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe will use the information you give us to publish a summary of your statement on the modern slavery statement registry. This will include a link to the full statement on your website.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"who-can-use-this-service\"\u003eWho can use this service?\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAny organisation that has created a modern slavery statement, including those that:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eare legally required to publish an annual modern slavery statement in the UK\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ehave chosen to publish a modern slavery statement voluntarily\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca class=\"gem-c-button govuk-button govuk-button--start\" role=\"button\" href=\"https://modern-slavery-statement-registry.service.gov.uk/sign-in/\"\u003e Start now \u003csvg class=\"govuk-button__start-icon govuk-!-display-none-print\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"17.5\" height=\"19\" viewbox=\"0 0 33 40\" role=\"presentation\" focusable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M0 0h13l20 20-20 20H0l20-20z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e",
